'''味觉感受器，类型2，成员14，TAS2R14''' 是一个人类基因组中''TAS2R14''基因编码的蛋白质，是苦味味觉感受器的一员<ref name="pmid10761934">{{cite journal | author = Adler E, Hoon MA, Mueller KL, Chandrashekar J, Ryba NJ, Zuker CS | title = A novel family of mammalian taste receptors | journal = Cell | volume = 100 | issue = 6 | pages = 693–702 | pmid = 10761934 | pmc =  | doi =10.1016/S0092-8674(00)80705-9  |date=Apr 2000}}</ref><ref name="pmid10766242">{{cite journal | author = Matsunami H, Montmayeur JP, Buck LB | title = A family of candidate taste receptors in human and mouse | journal = Nature | volume = 404 | issue = 6778 | pages = 601–4 | pmid = 10766242 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1038/35007072 |date=Apr 2000}}</ref><ref name="entrez">{{cite web | title = Entrez Gene: TAS2R14 taste receptor, type 2, member 14| url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=50840| accessdate = }}</ref>。

== 功能 ==
该基因所属的味觉感受器家族是G蛋白偶联受体超家族中的一员，其蛋白主要表达在舌头和腭的上皮味觉受体细胞中。它们是组织在基因组中的基因集群，在小鼠和人类中表达在苦味位点。在功能表达研究中，TAS2R14与(-)-α-[[侧柏酮|侧柏酮]]（[[苦艾酒|苦艾酒]]和{{le|印防己毒素|picrotoxin}}中的原发性神经毒性剂）相关<ref name="pmid15178431">{{cite journal | author = Behrens M, Brockhoff A, Kuhn C, Bufe B, Winnig M, Meyerhof W | title = The human taste receptor hTAS2R14 responds to a variety of different bitter compounds | journal = Biochem. Biophys. Res. Commun. | volume = 319 | issue = 2 | pages = 479–85 | pmid = 15178431 | doi = 10.1016/j.bbrc.2004.05.019 |date=June 2004}}</ref>。该基因所在的味觉感受器基因簇位于[[12号染色体|12号染色体]]短臂13带<ref name="entrez" />。

TAS2R14和其它几种苦味感受器也在人类呼吸道[[平滑肌|平滑肌]]细胞上表达。它们在这些细胞中的活化会导致细胞内[[钙|钙]]离子增加，从而触发[[钾离子通道|钾离子通道]]打开，使细胞膜[[超极化_(生物学)|超极化]]，平滑肌放松。因此，这些受体的活化会导致[[支气管扩张|支气管扩张]]。<ref name="pmid20972434">{{cite journal | author = Deshpande DA, Wang WC, McIlmoyle EL, Robinett KS, Schillinger RM, An SS, Sham JS, Liggett SB | title = Bitter taste receptors on airway smooth muscle bronchodilate by localized calcium signaling and reverse obstruction | journal = Nat. Med. | volume = 16 | issue = 11 | pages = 1299–304 | pmid = 20972434 | pmc = 3066567 | doi = 10.1038/nm.2237 |date=November 2010}}</ref>

